<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦不敢相信外面这么冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在休息时间，他穿了毛衣和外套，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>围了围巾，戴了帽子和手套。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是很冷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天在外面活动！穿厚一点。” 雪莉老师在伊坦走进门时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“外面？” 伊坦问，“但是太冷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好玩儿的。” 波比说，“你会习惯的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦不想在外面活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是拉上了外套拉链。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨晚下雪了，现在地上都是雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦穿着新靴子小心地走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不习惯在雪地里走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他害怕滑倒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在外面做什么？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有很多在雪里玩儿的方法！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要玩儿雪地拔河的游戏。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森和伊坦，你们一队。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比、尼娜、莉琪，你们一队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们一起选个队名和代表颜色。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为什么在女生队？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你拔河厉害吗？” 伊坦问贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很糟糕。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们就是糟糕队。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！好。我们队选绿色。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你们看看紫雏菊队的力量！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你们看看绿糟糕队的力量！” 贾森回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真不敢相信我们的队叫紫雏菊队。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“紫雏菊队，在雪里画一条线。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给尼娜一瓶紫色的液体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “雪地颜料，是食物色素和水的混合物。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“线要画在哪里呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一个卷尺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“两条线隔两米，每条线两米长。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦和尼娜在雪里画了线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是绳子的中心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师指着绳子上绑着的小旗，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先把小旗拉到自己的线的队伍赢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外一个规则是不能摔倒！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果有人摔倒，那个队伍就输！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦看了看自己的靴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不能摔倒？” 他担心地想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“排好队，准备好！” 雪莉老师喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最强的人在后面。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们可以的！” 伊坦小声对贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开始！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦马上感觉到一股很强的拉力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦和贾森跌跌撞撞地往前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦把靴子插进雪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他紧闭着眼睛，用力拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和贾森慢慢往后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小旗在往他们这边移动！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他更用力拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这时，紫雏菊队也用力地拉了一下！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦脚一滑，摔倒在雪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“紫雏菊队赢了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>绿糟糕队输了！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>摔倒在雪里其实没那么糟糕，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还很有意思！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来大喊：“再玩儿一次吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>